{"id": "1341473612112334918", "channel_id": "1341473612112334918", "type": 0, "author_id": "552061693455499275", "author_name": "yi.ming", "author_bot": false, "content": "如圖，增益卡“奇妙料理”依舊會增加費用，再次強調規則上寫的是“指令卡”不包含“增益卡”，即使這張增益卡只有珈倫能產出也一樣。\n\n我好奇其他喚醒體專屬的增益卡也會出現這種情況嗎？歡迎其他人補充他們遇到的狀況。", "timestamp": "2025-02-18T18:17:12.502000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-18T18:22:53.818000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1341473612481302528", "filename": "Screenshot_20250219_021224.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 146952, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1341473612112334918/1341473612481302528/Screenshot_20250219_021224.jpg?ex=6a00cba8&is=69ff7a28&hm=cf7cdc95b2faa56a6124d7287abaedf0fcf328b4a8e52ac5eed1e7d746ba9889&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341473612112334918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "算力調和還沒修好呢…", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1341393493536276562", "channel_id": "1341393493536276562", "type": 0, "author_id": "1264175553800573001", "author_name": "2041880926", "author_bot": false, "content": "(本人有點跟不上時代不好意思)\n大概知道被削弱了但是不知道確切是被削成怎樣(找不到通知 想知道被怎樣削了 超好奇)<:cry:1243502872021438475> \n看到有人說用尤烏的會出事?\n旺達我知道要積5層 但有時就會直接累積上去(BUG?", "timestamp": "2025-02-18T12:58:50.745000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341393493536276562", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融朵怎麼了?為啥有時旺達3費卡會返還不了算力?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168103141416960"]}
